title: Ebro In The Morning - Guest: Asher Roth
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Asher Roth joins Ebro in the Morning to discuss where he has been since finding fame with the track 'I Love College'. He also discusses his relationship w/ Justin Bieber, Scooter Braun, and Lil Yachty whether he would do a documentary & more.
